<h4>Setting It Up? Easy Peasy!</h4>
<p>Ditch those complex instruction manuals. Our intuitive design ensures you&#8217;ll have the strap ready on your Quest 3 in no time. Heck, even your little sibling or kid can do it. Seriously, give it a try!</p>
<p>Built to Last, But Super Flexible: We’re talking side straps that fold a whopping 180° and are crafted from super-strong POM polymer. And for those who like to tweak and twist things often, rest assured, these straps can take it.</p>
