<h4>No More “Face Squeeze” Moments</h4>
<p>Feel the magic of our top knob which spreads out that facial pressure. Plus, with the dual-knob setup, your VR headset will feel rock-solid. Many of you asked for a worthy upgrade from the Quest 3 elite strap. We think we’ve nailed it.</p>
<p>Cushioned Bliss: Get ready to treat your head with our plush cushions. Merging a springy memory foam pad with a sleek PU leather exterior, we&#8217;ve created something both comfortable and easy to keep clean.</p>
